        "action": "Abolish Inheritance Tax (Death Tax)",
        "additional_details": "Inheritance tax in many cases is a second tax on money that has already been taxed.\r\n \r\nThe inability to pass on the full value of one's savings, investments and property is adversely affecting a huge number of people.\r\n",
